nodes.text: Ku'Baku was a blue giant star. The primary of the Ku'Bakai system in the Outer Rim Territories, it was orbited by the planet Kubindi.

Ku'Baku first appeared in the Star Wars Legends continuity under the name Ku'Bakai. Ku'Baku was brought into the canon continuity in the 2015 magazine Star Wars: Build the Millennium Falcon 34, however the ai was changed to a u, changing the name from Ku'Bakai to Ku'Baku.
